const Page6 = props => { return (

Practicing coping strategies

Is there any part of any coping strategy that you want to practice together?

If your mentee says yes, practice with them for 10-15 minutes

Is there anything you need to help you use this strategy outside of mentoring?

Talk with your mentee about the help they need.
For example, you could help them think about setting reminders or using their toolkit.

) } export default Page6
